<P><PB REF="2" MS="Y">
A LETTER TO <HI>Richard</HI> Lord Bi&s;hop of <HI>Landaff,</HI> ON THE SUBJECT OF HIS LORDSHIP'S LETTER TO THE LATE ARCHBISHOP OF CANTERBURY.</P>
<P>BY RICHARD CUMBERLAND.</P>
<P>LONDON: Printed for CHARLES DILLY, in the Poultry; and J. WALTER, Charing-cro&s;s.</P>
